properties.description: Are you looking for a nice home in a green, centrally located, child-friendly environment? Then we have good news! This house on the DRUMELZIER is perfectly located and surrounded by greenery.

Here is another nice starter home. Modern kitchen, toilet and bathroom. The house is stylishly finished, completely contemporary. You can go in! An interesting middle house for starters and young families.

If interested, we are happy to take the time for you! Plan an appointment via our website and we will be happy to show you the home with a maximum of 2 people. If a physical appointment does not work out well, call for digital options!
